1. *Zaboraviš* da nam je danas rođendan. (You forgot that it's our birthday today.) 
2. *Zaboraviš* li da je sutra njegov rođendan? (Do you forget that tomorrow is his birthday?)
3. Ona *zaboravi* sve što je planirala da uradi. (She forgot everything she had planned to do.)
4. *Zaboravila* je da se zamoli za pomoć. (She forgot to ask for help.)
5. Oni su *zaboravili* da će im trebati dodatna pomoć. (They forgot that they would need additional help.)